external_knowledge:
- The ranking of recycling rates is based on the highest rate being the most desirable; 
- User roles and their distribution across departments can influence waste management strategies; 
- Regional comparison of recycling rates may reveal areas needing improvement.

sql:
SELECT SUM(yellow_bin_kg) AS total_yellow_bin_kg
FROM monthly_waste_data
WHERE month = '2023-01';

SELECT event_id, 
       (yellow_bin_collected_kg + red_bin_collected_kg + blue_bin_collected_kg + white_bin_collected_kg) AS total_collected_weight
FROM collection_events;

